G-derivations to fD.LG-derivations and vice versa: this provides the\nlink with operational semantics, given that every f.LG-derivation is in a\nCurry-Howard correspondence with a directional\n$\\overline\\lambda\\mu\\widetilde{\\mu}$-term.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 5 Nov 2020 15:13:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-06"}
